    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i understand, but my doctor is actually out of the office today and i can't get an appointment until next week. the headache is making it really hard to focus or even sleep. is there really that much of a risk if i just take one or two of the small 200mg tablets? it's not like i'm taking a whole bottle.",
